> **ƒê·ªÅ t√†i:** X√¢y d·ª±ng ·ª©ng d·ª•ng Front-end k·∫øt n·ªëi Binance API ƒë·ªÉ thi·∫øt k·∫ø thu·∫≠t to√°n t·ª± ƒë·ªông trading  
> **M√¥n h·ªçc:** C√¥ng ngh·ªá Ph·∫ßn m·ªÅm (SE2025) - Nh√≥m 9.4  
> **Chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c:** RSI + EMA v·ªõi Dynamic Position Sizing  
> **K·∫øt qu·∫£ Backtest:** +74.3% profit, 73.4% win rate (2 nƒÉm data)

