## üìñ T·ªïng quan

BinanceBot l√† h·ªá th·ªëng trading t·ª± ƒë·ªông to√†n di·ªán, k·∫øt h·ª£p gi·ªØa **Backend Trading Engine** (Python) v√† **Frontend Dashboard** (Vue 3), ƒë∆∞·ª£c thi·∫øt k·∫ø ƒë·ªÉ giao d·ªãch cryptocurrency tr√™n Binance Exchange m·ªôt c√°ch chuy√™n nghi·ªáp.

### üéØ M·ª•c ti√™u ƒë·ªÅ t√†i

1. **X√¢y d·ª±ng giao di·ªán web** tr·ª±c quan ƒë·ªÉ qu·∫£n l√Ω bot trading
2. **T√≠ch h·ª£p Binance API** cho vi·ªác thu th·∫≠p d·ªØ li·ªáu v√† th·ª±c hi·ªán giao d·ªãch
3. **Ph√°t tri·ªÉn thu·∫≠t to√°n trading** d·ª±a tr√™n c√°c ch·ªâ b√°o k·ªπ thu·∫≠t (RSI, EMA)
4. **Backtesting & Optimization** ƒë·ªÉ t·ªëi ∆∞u h√≥a chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c
5. **Risk Management** v·ªõi stop-loss, position sizing, ROI targets

### ‚ú® T√≠nh nƒÉng ch√≠nh

#### üéØ Trading Core (Backend)
- ‚úÖ **Live Trading** - Giao d·ªãch t·ª± ƒë·ªông 24/7 tr√™n Binance
- ‚úÖ **Paper Trading** - M√¥ ph·ªèng giao d·ªãch v·ªõi dry-run wallet (1000 USDT)
- ‚úÖ **Backtesting** - Test chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c v·ªõi 2+ nƒÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu l·ªãch s·ª≠
- ‚úÖ **Hyperopt** - T·ªëi ∆∞u tham s·ªë t·ª± ƒë·ªông (2000 epochs)
- ‚úÖ **25+ Strategies** - Th∆∞ vi·ªán chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c s·∫µn c√≥
- ‚úÖ **Risk Management** - Stop Loss (-12%), ROI Targets (20%/15%/10%/5%)

#### üé® Frontend Dashboard (UI)
- ‚úÖ **Dashboard** - T·ªïng quan t√†i kho·∫£n, balance, P&L
- ‚úÖ **Live Trading View** - Charts v·ªõi RSI/EMA indicators
- ‚úÖ **Backtest Results** - K·∫øt qu·∫£ backtest chi ti·∫øt v·ªõi charts
- ‚úÖ **Hyperopt Monitor** - Theo d√µi optimization real-time
- ‚úÖ **Settings** - Qu·∫£n l√Ω API keys, strategy params
- ‚úÖ **Binance Theme** - Giao di·ªán v√†ng ƒë·∫∑c tr∆∞ng c·ªßa Binance

#### üîß Technical Stack
- ‚úÖ **REST API + WebSocket** - Real-time communication
- ‚úÖ **SQLite Database** - L∆∞u tr·ªØ trade history
- ‚úÖ **CCXT Library** - Multi-exchange support
- ‚úÖ **TA-Lib** - Technical analysis indicators
- ‚úÖ **Docker Ready** - Containerized deployment

### üìä K·∫øt qu·∫£ Demo

**Backtest Period:** 01/01/2023 - 01/12/2025 (2 nƒÉm)  
**Chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c:** RSI_EMA v·ªõi Kelly Criterion Position Sizing  
**Timeframe:** 4h candlesticks

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| **Total Profit** | +742.73 USDT |
| **Profit %** | +74.27% |
| **Win Rate** | 73.42% (58/79 trades) |
| **Max Drawdown** | 14.65% |
| **Sharpe Ratio** | 2.31 |
| **Best Trade** | +98.65 USDT (OP/USDT) |
| **Avg Duration** | 13h 30m |

