---

## üöÄ C√†i ƒë·∫∑t

### Y√™u c·∫ßu h·ªá th·ªëng

```
Python >= 3.11
Node.js >= 18.x
npm >= 9.x
TA-Lib (Technical Analysis Library)
```

### B∆∞·ªõc 1: Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/dangdoday/SE2025-9.4.git
cd SE2025-9.4
```

### B∆∞·ªõc 2: Setup Backend (Python)

```bash
# T·∫°o virtual environment
python -m venv venv

# K√≠ch ho·∫°t venv
# Windows:
venv\Scripts\activate
# Linux/Mac:
source venv/bin/activate

# C√†i ƒë·∫∑t dependencies
pip install -r requirements/base.txt
pip install -r requirements/hyperopt.txt
pip install -r requirements/plot.txt

# C√†i TA-Lib (Windows)
pip install TA-Lib

# C√†i TA-Lib (Linux)
sudo apt-get install ta-lib
pip install TA-Lib

# C√†i TA-Lib (Mac)
brew install ta-lib
pip install TA-Lib
```

### B∆∞·ªõc 3: Setup Frontend (Vue 3)

```bash
cd binancebot-ui
npm install
```

### B∆∞·ªõc 4: C·∫•u h√¨nh API Keys

```bash
# Copy template
cp .env.example .env

# Ch·ªânh s·ª≠a .env
# BINANCE_API_KEY=your_key
# BINANCE_API_SECRET=your_secret
# DRY_RUN=true
# DRY_RUN_WALLET=1000
```

### B∆∞·ªõc 5: Download Data (Optional)

```bash
# Download 2 nƒÉm d·ªØ li·ªáu 4h
binancebot download-data \
  --exchange binance \
  --pairs BTC/USDT ETH/USDT BNB/USDT OP/USDT \
  --timeframe 4h \
  --days 730
```

### B∆∞·ªõc 6: Ch·∫°y h·ªá th·ªëng

```powershell
# C√°ch 1: S·ª≠ d·ª•ng PowerShell script (Windows)
.\start_dual_mode.ps1

# C√°ch 2: Ch·∫°y th·ªß c√¥ng
# Terminal 1 - Backend
binancebot trade --config config/config_ui_test.json --strategy RSI_EMA

# Terminal 2 - Frontend
cd binancebot-ui
npm run dev
```

**Truy c·∫≠p UI:** http://localhost:3000

---

## üí° H∆∞·ªõng d·∫´n s·ª≠ d·ª•ng

### 1. Backtesting

Test chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c v·ªõi d·ªØ li·ªáu l·ªãch s·ª≠:

```bash
binancebot backtesting \
  --strategy RSI_EMA \
  --config config/config_ui_test.json \
  --timeframe 4h \
  --timerange 20230101-20251201
```

**Output:**
```
Result for strategy RSI_EMA
============================================
| Total Profit         | 742.73 USDT (74.27%)|
| Win Rate             | 73.42% (58/79)      |
| Max Drawdown         | 14.65%              |
| Sharpe Ratio         | 2.31                |
| Avg Trade Duration   | 13h 30m             |
============================================
```

### 2. Hyperparameter Optimization

T·ªëi ∆∞u tham s·ªë t·ª± ƒë·ªông:

```bash
binancebot hyperopt \
  --strategy RSI_EMA \
  --config config/config_ui_test.json \
  --timeframe 4h \
  --timerange 20230101-20251201 \
  --epochs 2000 \
  --hyperopt-loss SharpeHyperOptLoss \
  --spaces buy sell \
  --min-trades 20 \
  -j 8
```

**Optimization Spaces:**
- `buy` - Entry parameters (RSI < 30)
- `sell` - Exit parameters (RSI > 70)
- `roi` - ROI table
- `stoploss` - Stop loss %
- `trailing` - Trailing stop

### 3. Paper Trading (Dry-run)

M√¥ ph·ªèng giao d·ªãch v·ªõi ti·ªÅn ·∫£o:

```bash
binancebot trade \
  --config config/config_ui_test.json \
  --strategy RSI_EMA \
  --dry-run
```

**Features:**
- Virtual wallet: 1000 USDT
- Real market data
- Simulated orders
- No real money risk

### 4. Live Trading ‚ö†Ô∏è

**C·∫¢NH B√ÅO: S·ª≠ d·ª•ng ti·ªÅn th·∫≠t!**

```bash
# ƒê·∫£m b·∫£o dry_run: false trong config
binancebot trade \
  --config config/config_binance.json \
  --strategy RSI_EMA
```

**Safety Checklist:**
- ‚úÖ Tested thoroughly v·ªõi backtest
- ‚úÖ Optimized v·ªõi hyperopt
- ‚úÖ Practiced v·ªõi dry-run
- ‚úÖ Start v·ªõi stake nh·ªè (30 USDT)
- ‚úÖ Max 1-3 open trades
- ‚úÖ API keys: trade only, no withdrawal

### 5. Frontend Dashboard

**Login:**
- URL: http://localhost:3000
- Username: `admin` (b·∫•t k·ª≥)
- Password: `123456` (b·∫•t k·ª≥, >= 6 k√Ω t·ª±)

**Features:**
- **Dashboard:** Balance, P&L, Win Rate
- **Live Trading:** Charts, Indicators, Trades
- **Backtest:** Results, Metrics, Charts
- **Hyperopt:** Monitor optimization progress
- **Settings:** API Keys, Strategy params

---

## üìä Chi·∫øn l∆∞·ª£c RSI_EMA

### Overview

**File:** `user_data/strategies/RSI_EMA.py`

**Concept:** K·∫øt h·ª£p RSI (momentum) v·ªõi EMA (trend) ƒë·ªÉ t√¨m ƒëi·ªÉm v√†o c√≥ x√°c su·∫•t cao.

### Indicators

```python
# RSI - Relative Strength Index (14 periods)
dataframe['rsi'] = ta.RSI(dataframe, timeperiod=14)

# EMA - Exponential Moving Average
dataframe['ema_fast'] = ta.EMA(dataframe, timeperiod=12)
dataframe['ema_slow'] = ta.EMA(dataframe, timeperiod=26)
```

### Entry Signal (Buy)

```python
(dataframe['rsi'] < 30) &                    # Oversold
(dataframe['ema_fast'] > dataframe['ema_slow']) &  # Uptrend
(dataframe['volume'] > 0)                    # Valid volume
```

**ƒêi·ªÅu ki·ªán:**
1. RSI < 30 ‚Üí Oversold (gi√° qu√° th·∫•p)
2. EMA Fast > EMA Slow ‚Üí Uptrend (xu h∆∞·ªõng tƒÉng)
3. Volume > 0 ‚Üí Giao d·ªãch h·ª£p l·ªá

### Exit Signal (Sell)

```python
(dataframe['rsi'] > 70) |                    # Overbought
(dataframe['ema_fast'] < dataframe['ema_slow'])   # Downtrend
```

**ƒêi·ªÅu ki·ªán:**
1. RSI > 70 ‚Üí Overbought (gi√° qu√° cao) HO·∫∂C
2. EMA Fast < EMA Slow ‚Üí Downtrend (xu h∆∞·ªõng gi·∫£m)

### Risk Management

```python
# Stop Loss
stoploss = -0.12  # -12% max loss

# ROI Targets
minimal_roi = {
    "0": 0.20,    # 20% immediately
    "30": 0.15,   # 15% after 30min
    "60": 0.10,   # 10% after 1h
    "120": 0.05   # 5% after 2h
}

# Position Sizing (Kelly Criterion)
# Dynamically adjusts stake based on win rate
```

### Performance (2023-2025)

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Total Profit | +742.73 USDT (+74.27%) |
| Win Rate | 73.42% (58/79) |
| Max Drawdown | 14.65% |
| Sharpe Ratio | 2.31 |
| Avg Duration | 13h 30m |
| Best Trade | +98.65 USDT (OP/USDT) |
| Worst Trade | -43.21 USDT (LINK/USDT) |

### Top Pairs

| Pair | Profit | Trades | Win Rate |
|------|--------|--------|----------|
| OP/USDT | +98.65 | 5 | 100% |
| XAI/USDT | +87.32 | 4 | 100% |
| MINA/USDT | +81.47 | 6 | 83.3% |
| IMX/USDT | +73.28 | 7 | 85.7% |
| FET/USDT | +65.19 | 8 | 75% |

---

## üé® Frontend UI

### Tech Stack

```
Vue 3 (Composition API)
TypeScript
Vite (Build tool)
PrimeVue (UI Library)
ECharts (Charts)
TailwindCSS (Styling)
Pinia (State Management)
Vue Router (Routing)
```

### Pages

#### 1. Dashboard (`/dashboard`)

**Features:**
- Balance display (USDT)
- Profit/Loss chart
- Win rate metrics
- Top performing pairs
- Recent trades table

#### 2. Live Trading (`/trade`)

**Features:**
- Candlestick chart (ECharts)
- RSI indicator overlay
- EMA lines (fast/slow)
- Open positions table
- Trade history
- Quick close buttons

#### 3. Backtest Results (`/backtest`)

**Features:**
- Equity curve chart
- Drawdown chart
- Performance metrics
- Exit reasons pie chart
- Per-pair table

#### 4. Hyperopt Monitor (`/hyperopt`)

**Features:**
- Real-time progress
- Best parameters display
- Optimization logs (mock)
- Top 10 results

#### 5. Settings (`/settings`)

**Tabs:**
- API Keys
- Strategy Params
- Risk Management
- Preferences

---

## ‚öôÔ∏è C·∫•u h√¨nh

### Main Config

**File:** `config/config_ui_test.json`

```json
{
  "max_open_trades": 10,
  "stake_currency": "USDT",
  "stake_amount": 30,
  "dry_run": true,
  "dry_run_wallet": 1000,
  
  "exchange": {
    "name": "binance",
    "key": "",
    "secret": "",
    "pair_whitelist": [
      "BTC/USDT", "ETH/USDT", "BNB/USDT",
      "OP/USDT", "XAI/USDT", "MINA/USDT"
    ]
  },
  
  "api_server": {
    "enabled": true,
    "listen_ip_address": "127.0.0.1",
    "listen_port": 8080,
    "CORS_origins": ["http://localhost:3000"]
  }
}
```

### Environment Variables

**File:** `.env`

```bash
BINANCE_API_KEY=your_api_key
BINANCE_API_SECRET=your_secret
DRY_RUN=true
DRY_RUN_WALLET=1000
API_SERVER_PORT=8080
```

---

## üß™ Testing

### Backend Tests

```bash
pip install -r requirements/dev.txt
pytest
pytest --cov=binancebot tests/
```

### Frontend Tests

```bash
cd binancebot-ui
npm run test:unit
npm run type-check
npm run lint
```

---

## üõ†Ô∏è Development

### Commit Convention

```
<type>(<scope>): <subject>

Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore
```

**Examples:**
```bash
git commit -m "feat(strategy): add RSI_EMA with kelly criterion"
git commit -m "fix(ui): resolve WebSocket timeout"
git commit -m "docs(readme): update installation guide"
```

### Adding New Strategy

1. Copy template:
```bash
cp user_data/strategies/SampleStrategy.py user_data/strategies/MyStrategy.py
```

2. Edit strategy logic

3. Test:
```bash
binancebot backtesting --strategy MyStrategy
```

4. Optimize:
```bash
binancebot hyperopt --strategy MyStrategy --epochs 1000
```

