## ‚ö†Ô∏è Disclaimer

**Cryptocurrency trading involves significant risk.**

- ‚ö†Ô∏è You can lose all your capital
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Past performance ‚â† future results
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Educational purposes only
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Not financial advice
- ‚ö†Ô∏è Use at your own risk

**Recommendations:**
- ‚úÖ Test on Testnet first
- ‚úÖ Start with paper trading
- ‚úÖ Use money you can afford to lose
- ‚úÖ Set strict stop-losses
- ‚úÖ Monitor regularly

**Liability:** Developers are NOT responsible for any financial losses.

